metadata.name: Winter surge
metadata.description:
Tanzawa-ÅŒyama Quasi-National Park, Kanagawa, Japan ---

Far above Kanagawa, far from the city, a soul braves the mountain in the dead of winter, searching for answers. Searching for inexpressible answers to unknown questions. Answers not expressed in words, but instead an answer that echoes in each footstep and the swirl of the trees.  
For perhaps the most real and astounding lessons in life are never communicated from person to person.
